            <characteristic typeId="21befb24-fc85-4f52-a745-64b2e48f8228" name="Description">Friendly units that have the Genestealer Cults Faction and are within 12&quot; of model equipped with the Icon of the Cult Ascendant have the Furious Charge special rule and may re-roll faile Morale, Pinning and Fear tests. In addition, models in the same unit as the Icon of the Cult Ascendant have +1 Attack while the bearer is alive.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
