          <characteristics>
            <characteristic typeId="21befb24-fc85-4f52-a745-64b2e48f8228" name="Description">If the bearer is involved in a challenge, their opponent must pass a Toughness test before any attacks are made. If the test is failed, that model immediately suffers a Wound with no saves of any kind allowed, and a -1 penalty to both their Initiative and Attacks (to a minimum of 1) until the end of the phase. The Scourge of Distant Stars has no effect on vehicles.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
