    <selectionEntry id="ca48-32fc-dc5f-fa06" name="The First Curse" hidden="false" collective="false" type="upgrade">
      <rules>
        <rule id="b459-c194-54ad-87d3" name="Strange Mutations" publicationId="f840-ed73-pubd1e1" page="90" hidden="false">
          <description>Before the start of the game, roll a dice a apply the following result to The First Curse&apos;s unit of Purestrain Genestealers for the duration of the game:
1) Flesh Hooks: The unit doesn&apos;t suffer the penalty to their Initiative for chraging enemies through difficult terrain.
2) Hardened Carapaces: The unit&apos;s Armour Save is increased to 4+.
3) Toxin Glands: The unit&apos;s Melee weapons have the Poisoned special rule.
4) Adrenal Sacs: The unit has the Rage special rule.
5) Feeder Tendrils: The unit has the Preferred Enemy special rule.
6) Perfect Killing Machine: Choose the result you wish to apply to the unit.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
      <selectionEntryGroups>
