    <selectionEntry type="model" import="true" name="Nexos" hidden="false" id="d8df-4c37-c4bd-d11d">
      <costs>
        <cost name="pts" typeId="points" value="50"/>
      </costs>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="Nexos" id="2bf3-a0ba-020f-54d6" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="9669-1227-6d4e-9b08"/>
        <infoLink name="Cult Ambush" id="fa42-40cf-4a32-debd" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="5e06-11ab-8ac6-6375"/>
        <infoLink name="Unquestioning Loyalty" id="9a82-258d-39a1-8670" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="890d-2f13-d09f-5149"/>
        <infoLink name="Return to the Shadows" id="743c-bbe4-fbe6-46cf" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="68a1-1058-e764-744e"/>
        <infoLink name="Gene-Sect" id="843a-dcc3-0688-db98" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="d857-0598-85e6-e08b"/>
      </infoLinks>
      <selectionEntries>
        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Autopistol" hidden="false" id="18a9-bcdc-42f8-7958">
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="false" id="5678-88ef-8ac9-7feb"/>
            <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="false" id="d36c-bd56-9370-01aa"/>
          </constraints>
          <infoLinks>
            <infoLink name="Autopistol" id="6727-6322-be9c-a60c" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="2481-001b-00f9-501b"/>
          </infoLinks>
        </selectionEntry>
        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Blasting Charges" hidden="false" id="7416-c87a-7ddc-69f9">
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="ad3f-62f9-e4c4-7d00" includeChildSelections="false"/>
            <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="0dd1-1606-647b-a655" includeChildSelections="false"/>
          </constraints>
          <infoLinks>
            <infoLink name="Assault Grenades" id="e5ba-02e7-e7f3-d98d" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="fdd8-1a5f-5722-d6ee"/>
          </infoLinks>
        </selectionEntry>
      </selectionEntries>
      <rules>
        <rule name="Cult infiltration" id="e863-961f-ce07-098a" hidden="false">
          <description>Once per turn at the start of your turn, if the Nexos passes a Leadership test, you may do one of the following, if he passes on a double 1 you may do both. However, if you roll a double 6, something has gone wrong! Your opponent may choose one of the effects on one of your units:


1. Re-roll one result on the Cult Ambush table.

2. After rolling a single Reserve Roll, modify it by +1 or -1.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="New Strategic Coordinator" id="4ec9-2c6d-fcb8-cdc0" hidden="false">
          <description>At the start of your turn, if the Nexos is within 3&quot; of a friendly Primus, Clamavus or Alphus Jackal, choose one friendly unit of Acolyte Hybrids, Neophyte Hybrids, Hybrid Metamorphs, or Atalan Jackals anywhere on the battlefield. That chosen unit is considered to be within range of one aura ability of the selected character until the start of your next turn.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="6d3a-9592-2ec0-482c" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="model" import="true" name="Clamavus" hidden="false" id="9f27-d955-feb3-b1a7">
      <costs>
        <cost name="pts" typeId="points" value="45"/>
      </costs>
      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="Clamvus" id="ebfd-d7ee-ee4a-89df" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="0d67-cbf2-c979-e799"/>
        <infoLink name="Gene-Sect" id="f248-f082-d397-37ad" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="d857-0598-85e6-e08b"/>
        <infoLink name="Cult Ambush" id="6170-caff-6c22-27fa" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="5e06-11ab-8ac6-6375"/>
        <infoLink name="Unquestioning Loyalty" id="0ea9-4ece-e33d-d181" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="890d-2f13-d09f-5149"/>
        <infoLink name="Return to the Shadows" id="9d8a-3ac2-39c6-fd1f" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="68a1-1058-e764-744e"/>
        <infoLink name="Independent Character" id="f613-21c0-8653-aa6a" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="ef3b-09c6-4024-cd37"/>
      </infoLinks>
      <selectionEntries>
        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Autopistol" hidden="false" id="6af6-1409-0135-f4f0">
          <infoLinks>
            <infoLink name="Autopistol" id="e19c-cf64-7fec-21a8" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="2481-001b-00f9-501b"/>
          </infoLinks>
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="e8c0-2cda-6c7f-63c9" includeChildSelections="false"/>
            <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="4a0d-6f88-d4b9-ae25" includeChildSelections="false"/>
          </constraints>
        </selectionEntry>
        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Blasting Charges" hidden="false" id="872b-dfa1-45d8-705b">
          <infoLinks>
            <infoLink name="Assault Grenades" id="be17-bc9b-86c3-6138" hidden="false" type="profile" targetId="fdd8-1a5f-5722-d6ee"/>
          </infoLinks>
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="0f92-82a3-46d7-c4fa" includeChildSelections="false"/>
            <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="c723-0bce-d41c-9349" includeChildSelections="false"/>
          </constraints>
        </selectionEntry>
      </selectionEntries>
      <rules>
        <rule name="Scrambler Array" id="88ef-450b-9ba0-0820" hidden="false">
          <description>At the start of your opponent’s turn, the Clamavus may attempt to activate the Scrambler Array by taking a Leadership test. If passed, you may do two of the following or if the test was passed on a double 1, you may do all. However, if you roll a double 6 the Clamavus loses control over the scrambler array and he and any unit he has joined becomes pinned:


1. Once during that turn, after your opponent rolls a Reserve Roll, you may modify the result by +1 or -1.
2. Once during that turn, after your opponent determines the arrival location of an outflanking unit, you may reroll that result.
3. Until the start of you next turn, all enemy units that choose to Deep Strike within 12&quot; of the Clamavus always scatter, even if the result would normally not scatter. This means when a hit is rolled, the unit scatters the way the arrow is pointing. If a unit has a rule that allows them to never scatter. The unit follows the normal rules of arriving from deep strike.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="Proclamation Hailer" id="24fd-9c74-be1d-a774" hidden="false">
          <description>Friendly units within 12&quot; of this model may fire normally when doing mission actions and may reroll all failed morale test while doing a mission action.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="ffba-0818-499d-f827" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
    </selectionEntry>
