      <rules>
        <rule name="Deploy Explosives" id="c25b-bab0-e68b-3b19" hidden="false">
          <description>Before the game starts, but before scout moves. The owner of this unit may deploy 3 miner markers, with the numbers 1, 2 and 3. The mines must be deployed in the following way:


The mines must be placed more than 12&apos;&apos; away for the enemy deployment zone, must be placed more than 12&apos;&apos; of each other and must be more than 6&apos;&apos; away from objective markers.


When the mines are deployed secretly write down which 2 mines that are functioning and 1 mine that is a dud.


When an enemy unit ends their a move (Normal move, run, charge, fallback, etc) within 3 inches of the marker show your opponent your note. If it was a dud nothing happens and the mine is removed. If it was functioning, check what unit type the affected unit is:


Non-vehicle models: Takes d3+3 strength 4 ap 4 hits.



Vehicle models: Roll a dice on a 1-2 the vehicle is shaken, on a 3-4 the vehicle suffers an engine damaged, on a 5-6 the vehicle becomes immobilized.


When resolved remove the mine marker.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
